OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782748079
OL,3,CManchester City appoint Enzo Maresca
OL,4,Cas new manager
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports Sports
OL,7,FCorrespondent David Chisnall takes a
OL,8,Flook at the new man in charge at the
OL,9,FEtihad.
OL,11,FEnzo Maresca has been appointed as new
OL,12,Fmanager of Manchester City - signing a
OL,13,Fthree-year deal until June 2029.
OL,15,FHe takes over from Pep Guardiola after
OL,16,Fthe Spaniard called time on a trophy-
OL,17,Fladen decade at the club.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
