PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782748079
OL,3,CManchester City appoint Enzo Maresca
OL,4,Cas new manager
OL,6,FMaresca, 46, returns to the club where
OL,7,Fhe had previously worked under
OL,8,FGuardiola as assistant during their
OL,9,Fhistoric treble winning season before
OL,10,Fgoing on to manage Leicester City and
OL,11,FChelsea.
OL,13,F"Manchester City is a Club I know very
OL,14,Fwell and to have the chance to manage
OL,15,Fthis team is a brilliant opportunity
OL,16,Ffor me," the Italian said.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
