FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782748079
OL,3,CManchester City appoint Enzo Maresca
OL,4,Cas new manager
OL,6,F"City is an incredibly well-run
OL,7,Ffootball Club. Everything they do is
OL,8,Finnovative, planned and purposeful.
OL,9,FFor a manager, that is a dream
OL,10,Fsituation. It provides the consistency
OL,11,FI need to do my job effectively.
OL,13,F"This will be my third spell here. I
OL,14,Fknow this Club, I know the demands and
OL,15,FI know the expectations.
OL,17,F"The quality of the people who work
OL,18,Fhere is what makes it so special, and
OL,19,FI want to thank them for showing faith
OL,20,Fin my ability.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782748079
OL,3,CManchester City appoint Enzo Maresca
OL,4,Cas new manager
OL,6,F"I cannot wait to start coaching the
OL,7,Fplayers. I want us to win, play good
OL,8,Ffootball and enjoy the pressure of
OL,9,Frepresenting Manchester City."
OL,11,FEnzo Maresca joined Chelsea in July
OL,12,F2024, winning the UEFA Conference
OL,13,FLeague and Club World Cup.
OL,15,FHe signed for Chelsea after winning
OL,16,Fpromotion to the Premier League with
OL,17,FLeicester City in April 2024.
OL,19,FThe Italian stepped down from his role
OL,20,Fat Chelsea after a breakdown in his
OL,21,Frelationship with the club's ownership.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
