FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782748079
OL,3,CManchester City appoint Enzo Maresca
OL,4,Cas new manager
OL,6,FHe ended his tenure at the London club
OL,7,Fwith just one win in his final seven
OL,8,Fgames.
OL,10,FHis appointment means the top two
OL,11,Fteams from this season's Premier
OL,12,FLeague will now both be coached by
OL,13,Fdisciples of Pep Guardiola, with
OL,14,FArsenal's Mikel Arteta also having
OL,15,Fworked as his assistant.
OL,17,FMaresca was the immediate favourite
OL,18,Ffor the position when Guardiola
OL,19,Fannounced he was leaving in the final
OL,20,Fweek of the 2025-26 campaign.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782748079
OL,3,CManchester City appoint Enzo Maresca
OL,4,Cas new manager
OL,6,FSpeculation over a possible return to
OL,7,FCity, where he was previously
OL,8,FGuardiola's assistant, had already
OL,9,Fbeen growing for several months.
OL,11,FGuardiola's 10 years at Manchester
OL,12,FCity saw him win 20 trophies,
OL,13,Fincluding six Premier League titles
OL,14,Fand the Champions League.
OL,16,FMaresca faces a tough challenge in
OL,17,Ffollowing the most successful manager
OL,18,Fin City's history, but his previous
OL,19,Fwork under Guardiola and familiarity
OL,20,Fwith the club made him the standout
OL,21,Fcandidate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
