PN,36407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782748079
OL,3,CManchester City appoint Enzo Maresca
OL,4,Cas new manager
OL,6,FManchester City Chairman Khaldoon Al
OL,7,FMubarak said: "Enzo is someone who has
OL,8,Falways sought out opportunities to
OL,9,Fchallenge himself and succeed in his
OL,10,Fmanagerial career.
OL,12,F"He brings a personality, passion and
OL,13,Fintelligence completely aligned to our
OL,14,Fneeds.
OL,16,F"He is re-joining an organisation that
OL,17,Fis entirely in lock-step with his
OL,18,Fambition and hunger for achievement
OL,19,Fand his return to Manchester City is
OL,20,Ftherefore a welcome natural next step
OL,21,Ffor both him and the Club.
OL,26,@oD@OOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
