PN,36408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782748079
OL,3,CManchester City appoint Enzo Maresca
OL,4,Cas new manager
OL,6,F"Enzo inherits a squad and football
OL,7,Forganisation perfectly suited to
OL,8,Freflect and evolve his brand of
OL,9,Ffootball, and we are all very much
OL,10,Flooking forward to seeing the impact
OL,11,Fhe can have in building further on the
OL,12,FClub's success.
OL,14,F"Welcome home Enzo."
OL,16,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,17,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,18,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,19,Four region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUvD@TO]
